gobblin.data.management.trash

Class TrashFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.data.management.trash.TrashFactory

  • public class TrashFactory
extends Object
    Factory for creating Trash instance. Will automatically use TestTrash if TRASH_TEST is true, MockTrash if SIMULATE is true, and ImmediateDeletionTrash if SKIP_TRASH is true. Otherwise, it will use ProxiedTrash or Trash.
